===Pronunciation===
roi'stər <!-- /rojˈstɾ/ I'm not familiar enough with IPA yet. -->
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔɪstə(r)|-ɔɪstə(r)]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#{{intransitive}} To engage in [[noisy]], [[drunken]], or [[riotous]] behavior.
#{{intransitive}} To [[walk]] with a [[swaying]] motion.

